# Import Organization

## Import Order

```typescript
// ✅ GOOD: Import order with blank lines between groups
// 1. React and React-related
import { FC, useMemo, useCallback } from 'react';
import { useTranslation } from 'react-i18next';
import { useRouteLoaderData } from 'react-router-dom';

// 2. ODS Components and Constants
import { Button, Input, Text } from '@ovhcloud/ods-react';
import { ODS_BUTTON_SIZE, ODS_ICON_NAME } from '@ovhcloud/ods-components';
import { OsdsButton, OsdsIcon } from '@ovhcloud/ods-components/react';
import { ODS_THEME_COLOR_INTENT } from '@ovhcloud/ods-common-theming';

// 3. Manager Libraries
import { TProject } from '@ovh-ux/manager-pci-common';
import { PageLayout, Notifications } from '@ovh-ux/manager-react-components';
import { ShellContext } from '@ovh-ux/manager-react-shell-client';
import { NAMESPACES } from '@ovh-ux/manager-common-translations';

// 4. Third-party libraries
import clsx from 'clsx';
import { Search } from 'lucide-react';

// 5. Internal imports (using @/ alias)
import { useInstances } from '@/data/hooks/instance/useInstances';
import { Breadcrumb } from '@/components/breadcrumb/Breadcrumb.component';
import { deps } from '@/deps/deps';
```

## Import Patterns

### Named vs Default Exports

```typescript
// ✅ GOOD: Named exports for components
export const ComponentName = () => { /* ... */ };

// ✅ GOOD: Default export for pages
export default function PageName() { /* ... */ }

// ✅ GOOD: Named exports for hooks
export const useHookName = () => { /* ... */ };

// ✅ GOOD: Named exports for types
export type TTypeName = { /* ... */ };
```

### Path Aliases

```typescript
// ✅ GOOD: Use @/ alias for internal imports
import { Component } from '@/components/Component.component';
import { useHook } from '@/hooks/useHook';
import { selectData } from '@/view-models/dataViewModel';
import { TType } from '@/types/Type.types';
import { deps } from '@/deps/deps';

// ❌ BAD: Relative paths for internal imports
import { Component } from '../../../components/Component.component';
```

### Library-Specific Patterns

```typescript
// ✅ GOOD: ODS React components
import { Button, Text, Input, FormField } from '@ovhcloud/ods-react';

// ✅ GOOD: ODS Web components
import { OsdsButton, OsdsIcon, OsdsCard } from '@ovhcloud/ods-components/react';

// ✅ GOOD: ODS Constants
import { ODS_BUTTON_SIZE, ODS_ICON_NAME, ODS_TEXT_PRESET } from '@ovhcloud/ods-components';

// ✅ GOOD: ODS Theming
import { ODS_THEME_COLOR_INTENT } from '@ovhcloud/ods-common-theming';

// ✅ GOOD: Manager React Components
import { PageLayout, Notifications, Title } from '@ovh-ux/manager-react-components';

// ✅ GOOD: Manager Shell Client
import { ShellContext, useOvhTracking } from '@ovh-ux/manager-react-shell-client';
```

## Best Practices

### Grouping
- Separate import groups with blank lines
- Group by: React → ODS → Manager libs → Third-party → Internal
- Keep related imports together within groups

### Path Aliases
- Always use `@/` for internal imports
- Configured in `tsconfig.json` paths

### Type Imports
- Import types with `import type` when possible
- Or use regular imports for types (TypeScript handles it)

### Side-Effect Imports
- CSS imports: `import './styles.scss';`
- Theme imports: `import '@ovhcloud/ods-themes/default';`
- Place at top of file or in main entry point
